df = read.csv('https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JorgeGuGo1221/Markdown-git/master/coffee-flavors.csv')
fig <- plot_ly()
fig <- fig %>% add_trace(
  type='sunburst',
  ids=df$ids,
  labels=df$labels,
  parents=df$parents,
  domain=list(column=1),
  maxdepth=2,
  insidetextorientation='radial'
)
fig
